                <h1>Name Change Background Check: What You Need to Know</h1>
                <p>When undergoing a name change, whether due to marriage, divorce, or personal choice, a background check is essential. This ensures all previous records, including criminal, credit, and employment histories, are accurately updated. Conducting a thorough check protects against identity theft and assures that your new identity is secure and credible.</p>
